## Sensitive Data

### Never Log Secrets

```python
# BAD
logger.info("Connecting to service", api_key=config.api_key)

# GOOD
logger.info("Connecting to service", api_key_last4=config.api_key[-4:])
```

### Mask PII and Sensitive Details

```python
def mask_identifier(value: str) -> str:
    """Mask identifier for logging."""
    return f"***{value[-4:]}"

logger.info("Account updated",
            account=mask_identifier(account_id),
            action="settings_change")
```

