## Decision Chains (Cross-Module Correlation)

For tracing purposes, link related events using a correlation ID:

```python
# 1. Request received
logger.info("Request received", correlation_id="cor_123", action="create_item")

# 2. Validation passed
logger.info("Validation passed", correlation_id="cor_123", valid=True)

# 3. Processing started
logger.info("Processing started", correlation_id="cor_123", processor="default")

# 4. Processing complete
logger.info("Processing complete", correlation_id="cor_123", result="success")
```

### Generating Correlation IDs

```python
import uuid
from datetime import datetime

def generate_correlation_id() -> str:
    """Generate unique correlation ID."""
    timestamp = datetime.utcnow().strftime("%Y%m%d%H%M%S")
    short_uuid = uuid.uuid4().hex[:8]
    return f"cor_{timestamp}_{short_uuid}"
```

